(149, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 8283, 1, 0, 1200, 100, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 10, 10, 1, 'Mages who specialize in arcane magics truly understand the power bestowed within this ancient art. These robes were tailored by your fellow player, Trydeth!', 'None', 'co', 'Armor', 'None', 'TrydethsArcanist.swf', 'iwarmor', 'TrydethsArcanist', 'Arcanist Robes', '', -1),
(150, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 8283, 1, 0, 1200, 100, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 10, 10, 1, 'In the near future, symbiotes forge their armor out of bits and pieces of magnetized scrap metal. This literal attractive armor was inspired by your fellow player, Reddy!', 'None', 'co', 'Armor', 'None', 'Magnetic.swf', 'iwarmor', 'Magnetic', 'Magnetic Plate', '', -1),
(155, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 8283, 1, 0, 1200, 100, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 10, 13, 1, 'No one knows what gate this fiendish wraith is guarding...but no one has been brave enough to ever find out. The runes are color custom to match your devious soul. Inspired by your fellow player, Revontheus!', 'None', 'co', 'Armor', 'None', 'GateKeeper.swf', 'iwarmor', 'GateKeeper', 'Gate Keeper', '', -1),
(134, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 8283, 1, 0, 1200, 100, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 10, 10, 1, 'This armor once belonged to a powerful Norse Viking. Pairs nicely with the Horned Helm. Made by Lavitz, your fellow player.', 'None', 'co', 'Armor', 'None', 'Lavitz_skin.swf', 'iwarmor', 'Lavitz', 'Lavitz Viking Armor', '', -1),
(173, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 8283, 1, 0, 1200, 100, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 10, 10, 1, 'Horrific warrior of the Frozen Legion, this barbaric armor was created by your fellow player, Dage the Evil!', 'None', 'co', 'Armor', 'None', 'UndeadWarrior_skin.swf', 'iwarmor', 'UndeadWarrior', 'Undead Warrior', '', -1),
(126, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 8283, 1, 0, 1200, 100, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 104, 10, 1, 'This armor actually manipulates gravity itself! This armor was inspired by art created by your fellow player Gsog.', 'None', 'co', 'Armor', 'None', 'gravity_skin.swf', 'iwarmor', 'Gravity1', 'Gravity Overlord', '', -1),
(129, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 8283, 1, 0, 1500, 100, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 10, 10, 1, 'This is the armor of a legendary warrior, which the faith on dedication and honor changed the way a whole nation thinks.  Armor design inspired by RedWolf EADS.', 'None', 'co', 'Armor', 'None', 'Samurai2_skin.swf', 'iwarmor', 'Samurai2', 'Samurai Armor', '', -1),
(146, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 8283, 1, 0, 20000, 100, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 10, 10, 1, 'This armor is hot, hot, HOT! Fire is the only element responsible for life and death simultaneously. Inspired by player KittiKataklysm.', 'None', 'co', 'Armor', 'None', 'Inferno_skin.swf', 'iwarmor', 'Inferno', 'Inferno', '', -1),
(215, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 1, 8283, 1, 0, 21000, 100, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 10, 13, 1, 'A gilded armor for a golden hero, you''ll outshine your enemies with this awesome plate designed by Blake Don.', 'None', 'co', 'Armor', 'None', 'Banisher.swf', 'iwarmor', 'Banisher', 'Banisher Armor', '', -1),
(204, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 1, 8283, 1, 0, 25000, 100, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 10, 13, 1, 'This regal armor embodies the savage ferocity of the wolves that roam Lore. Forged by Royal Knight, the Royal Fang Armor offers great protection while giving your enemies something to howl about!', 'None', 'co', 'Armor', 'None', 'RoyalFang.swf', 'iwarmor', 'RoyalFang', 'Royal Fang Armor', '', -1),
(157, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 8283, 1, 0, 27000, 100, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 10, 13, 1, 'No one knows what the Shadow Ghoul is. Undead... living... all we know is that it is something not from this world. This fully color-custom monstrosity was discovered by your fellow player, Kris Clean.', 'None', 'co', 'Armor', 'None', 'MiltonPoolGhoul1_skin.swf', 'iwarmor', 'MiltonPoolGhoul1', 'Shadow Ghoul', '', -1),
(206, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 8283, 1, 0, 27777, 100, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 10, 13, 1, 'Donning this armor designed by RazzleDazzle gives you an insatiable appetite for the stuff of nightmares. You become what everyone fears, and this pleases you. You are now a TerrorLord, and terror is just what you''ll bring!', 'None', 'co', 'Armor', 'None', 'TerrorLord.swf', 'iwarmor', 'TerrorLord', 'Terror Lord', '', -1),
(196, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 1, 0, 30000, 100, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 10, 13, 1, 'Thanks to enven, You''ll be a knight in shining platemail when you equip this awesome silver armor! All you need is a white charger and a steel blade before you''re ready to rescue damsels- or dudes- in distress!', 'None', 'co', 'Armor', 'None', 'SilverGunSmith.swf', 'iwarmor', 'SilverGunSmith', 'Silver GunSmith', '', -1),
(230, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 1, 0, 35000, 100, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 10, 13, 1, 'Fused with your spirit orb, this armor is intended to keep you safe while fueling your war-rage, making you a much more effective warrior. Designed by soulsyth.', 'None', 'co', 'Armor', 'None', 'SoulKnight.swf', 'iwarmor', 'SoulKnight', 'SoulKnight', '', -1),
(261, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 1, 0, 35000, 100, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 10, 13, 1, 'Medieval Shadow-shapers used this armor to curse knights of lesser houses from stealing the glory of their lords. Perhaps Dudulokinho was one once?', 'None', 'co', 'Armor', 'None', 'MedievalShadow1.swf', 'iwarmor', 'MedievalShadow', 'Medieval Shadow', '', -1),
(268, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 1, 0, 37500, 100, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 10, 13, 1, 'Dissatisfied with the Zealith Reaver, Agyron added some major modifications to truley awaken it''s potential. Even Zealith himself would think twice before attacking you.', 'None', 'co', 'Armor', 'None', 'ZelithWarrior1.swf', 'iwarmor', 'ZelithWarrior1', 'Zealith Warrior', '', -1),
(280, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 1, 0, 38500, 100, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 10, 13, 1, 'Want to know every weakness and every fear of your enemy?  Take on the mantle of Enchanter and know your enemy.  Then use your knowledge.  Discovered by Digyo, this armor will unnerve even the strongest fighter.', 'None', 'co', 'Armor', 'None', 'Enchanter.swf', 'iwarmor', 'Enchanter', 'Enchanter', '', -1),
(232, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 45000, 100, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 10, 13, 1, 'Designed by _Aegis_, this armor epitomizes the UnderWorld. Terrify your opponents with thoughts of descending into the Darkness, never to return again!', 'None', 'co', 'Armor', 'None', 'DeathsHand.swf', 'iwarmor', 'DeathsHand', 'Death''s Hand Armor', '', -1),
(263, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 45000, 100, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 10, 13, 1, 'The origins of this otherworldly armor are...well, unknown. But theavenger07 may know!', 'None', 'co', 'Armor', 'None', 'TheUnknown.swf', 'iwarmor', 'TheUnknown', 'The Unknown', '', -1),
(284, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 1, 0, 50000, 100, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 10, 13, 1, 'You may have guards and maids to do your bidding but you also like to get your hands dirty! Crafted by the Hero that goes by Royal Knight.', 'None', 'co', 'Armor', 'None', 'ArmoredRoyalPrince.swf', 'iwarmor', 'ArmoredRoyalPrince', 'Armored Royal Prince', '', -1);
