(239, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 1, 0, 50000, 100, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 10, 13, 1, 'Crafted by _Aegis_, only the most noble and upright warriors feel comfortable in this most Good of armors. Wear it well, Hero, and remember to always fight on the side of right!', 'None', 'co', 'Armor', 'None', 'AngelChamp.swf', 'iwarmor', 'AngelChamp', 'Angel Champion', '', -1),
(257, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 1, 0, 50000, 100, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 10, 13, 1, 'Gompa, reknowned battle-armorer, crafted this cunning and decidedly chill-resistant armor to keep the cold out in the midst of even the most heated battles!', 'None', 'co', 'Armor', 'None', 'gompaarmor.swf', 'iwarmor', 'gompaarmor', 'Snowstorm', '', -1),
(213, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 55000, 100, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 10, 13, 1, 'Hand-crafted by Laken himself, this formal attire is well suited for special occasions and epic boss battles.', 'None', 'co', 'Armor', 'None', 'LakenFormalSuit.swf', 'iwarmor', 'LakenFormalSuit', 'Laken Formal Suit', '', -1),
(202, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 75000, 100, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 10, 13, 1, 'Drakonus crafted this armor to be seemingly made of bones. It is in fact made of very powerful and very enchanted metals, found deep underground. It provides superb protection, both physical and magical.', 'None', 'co', 'Armor', 'None', 'Vengence.swf', 'iwarmor', 'Vengence', 'Vengeance', '', -1),
(190, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 1, 0, 75000, 100, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 10, 13, 1, 'Constructed by the infamous armor-crafter, Reddy, this Exo Skin will be sure to scare the sweet bejoneses out of any enemies you come across.', 'None', 'co', 'Armor', 'None', 'ExoSkin.swf', 'iwarmor', 'ExoSkin', 'ExoSkin', '', -1),
(133, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 1, 0, 300000, 100, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 10, 10, 1, 'An elusive assassin sect, the Armored Hashashin was built for victory and created by your fellow player, Rohan!', 'None', 'co', 'Armor', 'None', 'Hashashin1_skin.swf', 'iwarmor', 'Hashashin1', 'Armored Hashashin Armor', '', -1),
(132, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 500000, 100, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 10, 10, 1, 'An elusive sect of assassins, the Hashashin Armor was built for stealth and designed by your fellow player, Rohan!', 'None', 'co', 'Armor', 'None', 'Hashashin2_skin.swf', 'iwarmor', 'Hashashin2', 'Hashashin Armor', '', -1),
(153, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 1856, 1, 0, 600, 100, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 10, 10, 1, 'Forged from bronze and modified with an enhanced core, the mysterious Axe of Minar was inspired by--and named after--your fellow player, Minar!', 'None', 'Weapon', 'Axe', 'None', 'items/axes/AxeofMinar.swf', 'iwaxe', 'AxeofMinar', 'Axe of Minar', '', -1),
(179, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 1, 1856, 1, 0, 25000, 100, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 10, 10, 1, 'Tera Wind forged this massive battleaxe using steampunk technology. It is as much of a steampunk symbol as it is a ruthless display of power.', 'None', 'Weapon', 'Axe', 'None', 'items/axes/HeavySteampunkAxe.swf', 'iwaxe', 'HeavySteampunkAxe', 'Heavy Steampunk Axe', '', -1),
(278, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 1957, 1, 0, 100, 100, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 10, 13, 1, 'There''s power in literature, and in this case, more power at your fingertips than you can imagine.  These books, all the knowledge you can ever hope to have, will accompany you forevermore. Brought to you by Championaustin.', 'None', 'ba', 'Cape', 'None', 'items/capes/BooksOfPower.swf', 'iicape', 'BooksOfPower', 'Books Of Power', '', -1),
(229, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 1957, 1, 0, 100, 100, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 10, 13, 1, 'Some necromancer must have just wired bone to bone to create this intimidating bonewing cape! Designed by Ninjudo.', 'None', 'ba', 'Cape', 'None', 'items/capes/ninjudoCape.swf', 'iicape', 'NinjudoCape', 'Demonic Nemesis Cape', '', -1),
(293, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 1957, 1, 0, 125, 100, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 10, 13, 1, 'Stay fierce against the competition with this tiger tail! (It is Color Custom!) Suggested by Godz 4 gs!', 'None', 'ba', 'Cape', 'None', 'items/capes/CCTigerTail.swf', 'iicape', 'CCTigerTail', 'Tiger Tail', '', -1),
(265, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 1957, 1, 0, 150, 100, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 10, 35, 1, 'All assassins could use extra knives in an easy to reach cape! Thus goes the motto of Lord SlayR.', 'None', 'ba', 'Cape', 'None', 'items/capes/BackBladesOfAssassins.swf', 'iicape', 'BackBladesOfAssassins', 'Backblades of Assassins', '', -1),
(235, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 1957, 1, 0, 10000, 100, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 10, 13, 1, 'These flaming wings of destruction were designed by Outlaw13th for all those who battle on outside the law!', 'None', 'ba', 'Cape', 'None', 'items/capes/DoomWings.swf', 'iicape', 'DoomWings', 'DoomWings', '', -1),
(197, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 1, 1957, 1, 0, 15000, 100, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 10, 13, 1, 'Crafted by enven, these wings will shine down on your friends, glowing with a beneficent light which will lead them to victory!', 'None', 'ba', 'Cape', 'None', 'items/capes/SilverGunSmithWings.swf', 'iicape', 'SilverGunSmithWings', 'Silver Gunsmith Wings', '', -1),
(238, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 1, 1957, 1, 0, 20000, 100, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 10, 13, 1, 'Designed by _Aegis_, these stunning wings will stretch out behind you as you run, lending you an aura of speed, grace, and agility.', 'None', 'ba', 'Cape', 'None', 'items/capes/AngelChampWings.swf', 'iicape', 'AngelChampWings', 'Angel Champion Wings', '', -1),
(127, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 1, 1957, 1, 0, 500000, 100, 1, 1, 0, 0, 100, 10, 10, 1, 'Rocks float aimlessly next to you. Idea inspired by Gsog.', 'None', 'ba', 'Cape', 'None', 'items/capes/gravityrocks1.swf', 'iicape', 'gravityrocks1', 'Gravity Cloak', '', -1),
(277, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 1856, 1, 0, 200, 100, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 10, 13, 1, 'CervantesMaxi discovered this dagger embedded in the very bones of Lore.  With massive strength, he ripped it from the rock and presents it to you as reminder of the power that one can wield if you only put your mind to it.', 'None', 'Weapon', 'Dagger', 'None', 'items/daggers/SarazenArmaments.swf', 'iwdagger', 'SarazenArmaments', 'Sarazen Armaments', '', -1),
(188, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 1856, 1, 0, 500, 100, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 10, 13, 1, 'These brilliantly gleaming daggers were crafted by Vampire Max in order to honor one of the most prevalent gods of the SandSea, and to ensure that he continues to let the sun shine down on their desert.', 'None', 'Weapon', 'Dagger', 'None', 'items/daggers/AmonRaDaggers.swf', 'iwdagger', 'AmonRaDaggers', 'Amon Ra Daggers', '', -1),
(180, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 1856, 1, 0, 550, 100, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 10, 10, 1, 'Vampire Max crafted this blade to take advantage of his Dark Gift. This blade causes vampires to enter a blood-craving frenzy, becoming much stronger and faster than before. The sword stores any blood that was drawn inside for the wielder''s later consumption.', 'None', 'Weapon', 'Dagger', 'None', 'items/swords/VampiresBlaze.swf', 'iwdagger', 'VampiresBlaze', 'Blood Blaze of the Vampire', '', -1),
(152, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 1856, 1, 0, 670, 100, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 10, 10, 1, 'Infused with the fury of the sun gods, these ancient daggers have withstood the test of time... and abrasive sandstorms. These weapons were inspired by your fellow player, Minar!', 'None', 'Weapon', 'Dagger', 'None', 'items/daggers/DaggerofRa.swf', 'iwdagger', 'DaggerofRa', 'Daggers of Ra', '', -1),
(158, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 1856, 1, 0, 9000, 100, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 10, 11, 1, 'A pair of mammoth blades capable of taking out any threat, forged by your fellow player RazzleDazzle!', 'None', 'Weapon', 'Dagger', 'None', 'items/daggers/RazzleDazzleBlade.swf', 'iwdagger', 'RazzleDazzleBlade', 'RazzleDazzle Daggers', '', -1),
(198, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 1, 1856, 1, 0, 10000, 100, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 10, 13, 1, 'Enven crafted these deadly silver duel busters to help you blast your enemies to bits!', 'None', 'Weapon', 'Dagger', 'None', 'items/guns/SilverSmithedGun.swf', 'iwdagger', 'SilverSmithedGun', 'Silver Duel Busters', '', -1),
(219, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 1, 1856, 1, 0, 10000, 100, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 10, 13, 1, 'There once ruled a Queen, beautiful and kind. But twisted magics changed her personality and yes, even her very soul. This blade was used to relieve the people of her reign, and was wielded and crafted by the mighty hero, evokersoul.', 'None', 'Weapon', 'Dagger', 'None', 'items/swords/TyrantQueensSupression.swf', 'iwdagger', 'TyrantQueensSupression', 'Tyrant Queen''s Suppression', '', -1),
(223, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 1, 1856, 1, 0, 10000, 100, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 10, 13, 1, 'It looks like Vampire Max has just released the hottest hand-held SmartScythes in all of Lore! Download yours today!', 'None', 'Weapon', 'Dagger', 'None', 'items/daggers/DigitalTerror.swf', 'iwdagger', 'DigitalTerror', 'Digital Terror', '', -1),
(266, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 1, 1856, 1, 0, 16000, 100, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 10, 13, 1, 'Crafted by the mysterious Na Tra, these weapons will harness the fury inside of you and channel it into daggers of flame!', 'None', 'Weapon', 'Dagger', 'None', 'items/daggers/RagingFire.swf', 'iwdagger', 'RagingFire', 'Raging Fire Daggers', '', -1),
(270, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 1, 1856, 1, 0, 20000, 100, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 10, 13, 1, 'Let off a little steam with this combination designed by Redwolf EADS.  Watch that gauge though, for if your sheer awesomeness is too much, you may do more damage than you anticipate... to walls, houses, trees, paths.  Oh, and let''s not even imagine what the enemy will look like afterwards...', 'None', 'Weapon', 'Dagger', 'None', 'items/daggers/SteampunkBladedCannonAndShield.swf', 'iwdagger', 'SteampunkBladedCannonAndShield', 'Bladed Cannon and Shield', '', -1),
(167, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 1856, 1, 0, 22000, 100, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 10, 10, 1, 'A pair of devious daggers crated from strange organic materials not from this world. Perhaps Evokersoul may be able to provide some of this weapon''s history?', 'None', 'Weapon', 'Dagger', 'None', 'items/swords/EvokerSoulBlade.swf', 'iwdagger', 'EvokerSoulBlade', 'Evoker of Souls', '', -1),
(252, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 1, 1856, 1, 0, 25000, 100, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 10, 13, 1, 'Designed by the famed armorer, Darkondrago, these daggers will delight you, but inspire dread in even the deadliest of foes!', 'None', 'Weapon', 'Dagger', 'None', 'items/daggers/ThSoulStealerAdvanced.swf', 'iwdagger', 'ThSoulStealerAdvanced', 'Soul Stealer Advanced', '', -1),
(193, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 1, 1856, 1, 0, 33000, 100, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 10, 13, 1, 'Often used in ceremonial rituals, these ornate daggers are as beautiful and detailed as they are deadly. It is believed that Mieteor crafted these relics by hand without the use of magic.', 'None', 'Weapon', 'Dagger', 'None', 'items/daggers/DualDragonSlayers.swf', 'iwdagger', 'DualDragonSlayers', 'Dual DragonSlayers', '', -1),
(208, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 1856, 1, 0, 35000, 100, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 10, 13, 1, 'Inspired by Dorene, these savage maulers can serve many functions. Would you rather tear into your opponent with sharp claws, or slice them up with the wristblades? The choice is yours!', 'None', 'Weapon', 'Dagger', 'None', 'items/daggers/GiaWolfClaw.swf', 'iwdagger', 'GiaWolfClaw', 'Gia''s Primal Brawlers', '', -1),
(248, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 1, 1856, 1, 0, 35000, 100, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 10, 13, 1, 'Made of enchanted ice from the Northlands mixed with Frost Wyrm breath, this blade will chill your enemies to the core! Crafted by paultaker.', 'None', 'Weapon', 'Dagger', 'None', 'items/swords/DualFrostBreath.swf', 'iwdagger', 'DualFrostBreath', 'Dual Frost Breath', '', -1),
(243, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 1, 1856, 1, 0, 50000, 100, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 10, 13, 1, 'Reki knows his blades, and to prove it, he''s crafted a dual-wielding sword set to showcase his skill. Bear them well, Hero!', 'None', 'Weapon', 'Dagger', 'None', 'items/daggers/RekiTwinDragons.swf', 'iwdagger', 'RekiTwinDragons', 'Reki''s Twin Dragons', '', -1),
(169, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 1856, 1, 0, 90000, 100, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 10, 10, 1, 'Never let a kill go to waste -- so your fellow player Terosin believes! A massive pair of blades crafted from the bony remains of many unfortunate beasts.', 'None', 'Weapon', 'Dagger', 'None', 'items/swords/Terosinsword01.swf', 'iwdagger', 'Terosinsword01', 'Dual Terosin', '', -1),
(199, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 1, 1856, 1, 0, 15000, 100, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 10, 13, 1, 'Crafted by enven, this versatile weapon will appeal to both ranged and melee weapons alike! And all finished with a silvery patina for the refined gunblade user!', 'None', 'Weapon', 'Gun', 'None', 'items/guns/SilverSmithedGunblade.swf', 'iwgun', 'SilverSmithedGunblade', 'Silver-smithed Gunblade', '', -1),
(168, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 1856, 1, 0, 16500, 100, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 10, 10, 1, 'An ancient gun repaired by your fellow player Reki after being lost in the sands of time. This combination of dagger and pistol collects sunlight and bends it into a concentrated beam of light. The mechanism to focus light is missing a piece, however.', 'None', 'Weapon', 'Gun', 'None', 'items/guns/RekiGun.swf', 'iwgun', 'RekiGun', 'Piercing Light', '', -1),
(258, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 1, 1856, 1, 0, 20000, 100, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 10, 13, 1, 'Wileded by the legendary Hero xserenax, this bow was crafted in the image of her favorite, most trustworthy weapon!', 'None', 'Weapon', 'Gun', 'None', 'items/bows/LegendaryBow.swf', 'iwgun', 'LegendaryBow', 'Legendary Bow', '', -1),
(220, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 1956, 1, 0, 50, 100, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 10, 13, 1, 'Long used as a symbol of healing, this red mask is a beacon to all the wounded fighters on the field. Seeing this, they know that both a warrior and a healer are in their midst, and that they will soon know relief. Designed by DarkonDrago.', 'None', 'he', 'Helm', 'None', 'items/helms/CrossBerserkerMask.swf', 'iihelm', 'CrossBerserkerMask', 'Cross Berserker Mask', '', -1),
