(275, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 1856, 1, 0, 13000, 100, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 10, 13, 1, 'Dare you test your fortitude, Hero?  Dare you take up the sword that seems to boast its prowess, bloodstained and disturbed?  Look closely at this mighty blade created by disturbed indestructible and feel yourself shiver.  You shiver because you know what comes next...', 'None', 'Weapon', 'Sword', 'None', 'items/swords/DisturbedBlade.swf', 'iwsword', 'DisturbedBlade', 'Disturbed Blade', '', -1),
(187, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 1856, 1, 0, 15000, 100, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 10, 13, 1, 'One of the greatest mage-smiths in Lore, Wolf Bane solidified fire itself to form the core of this shining blade. You''ll really be able to turn the heat up on your monster attacks with THIS sword!', 'None', 'Weapon', 'Sword', 'None', 'items/swords/GreatFireBlade.swf', 'iwsword', 'GreatFireBlade', 'Great Fire Blade', '', -1),
(163, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 1856, 1, 0, 15000, 100, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 10, 10, 1, 'While a powerful blade had been forged, Max Man58 felt his creation needed more. Trapping the soul of the most powerful demon he could find inside the blade''s cold steel, it now hungers for anything living. The blade is as dangerous to your enemies as it is to you.', 'None', 'Weapon', 'Sword', 'None', 'items/swords/DemonicDevourer.swf', 'iwsword', 'DemonicDevourer', 'Demonic Devourer', '', -1),
