(271, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 1, 1856, 1, 0, 20000, 100, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 10, 13, 1, 'Smooth, cool and mysterious, the runes on this blade glow with the fortitude you need to get through your battle.  No matter what you go through, what you endure, this sword, designed by Hero Demon, will bring you a renewal of strength, purpose and life after each battle.', 'None', 'Weapon', 'Sword', 'None', 'items/swords/SoulBaneOfNewLife.swf', 'iwsword', 'SoulBaneOfNewLife', 'SoulBane of New Life', '', -1),
